 style=\"color:#004d86\">(Công ty cổ phần dịch vụ cáp treo Bà Nà (BANACAP)</span></strong></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#004d86\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://quantri.thanhdo.edu.vn/upload/thanhdo/images/DN10.jpg\" style=\"height:149px; width:300px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://quantri.thanhdo.edu.vn/upload/thanhdo/images/image009.png\" style=\"height:100px; width:300px\">&nbsp;</span></strong><br>\r\n<em><strong><span style=\"color:#004d86\">(Tập đoàn khách sạn Intercontinental tại Việt Nam)</span></strong></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://quantri.thanhdo.edu.vn/upload/thanhdo/images/DN11.jpg\" style=\"height:170px; width:300px\"><br>\r\n<em><strong><span style=\"color:#004d86\">(Tập đoàn khách sạn Novotel Suites tại Việt Nam)</span></strong></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#004d86\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://quantri.thanhdo.edu.vn/upload/thanhdo/images/DN12.jpg\" style=\"height:167px; width:300px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://quantri.thanhdo.edu.vn/upload/thanhdo/images/t%E1%BA%ADp%20%C4%91o%C3%A0n%20Elite%20PR%20school.jpg\" style=\"height:140px; width:300px\"></span></strong><br>\r\n<em><strong><span style=\"color:#004d86\">(Trường đào tạo doanh nhân và quản trị doanh nghiệp Elite PR school)</span></strong></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://quantri.thanhdo.edu.